History:Also sometimes referred to as the Hermes III, this is a variant of the Hermes II. It solely appeared in the Draconis Combine, suggesting that it was an export-only version. (The HER-4K Hermes III should not be confused with the HER-4K variant of the Hermes, which was an export version for the Draconis Combine of the Hermes II's predecessor.)



